data.description: Diamond in the Rough: Fixer Upper Opportunity! Embark on a total transformation with this 1500 sq ft 2 bedroom 2.5 bathroom fixer-upper that's a rehab project ready for a creative touch.  The main floor has high ceilings and an open concept. The second floor has the same open concept with interior and exterior access.  Conveniently located close to Rte. 93 this property is an ideal combination of location and renovation potential.  Property is being sold AS IS, as seen with all its faults.
